===Proper noun===
'''Gilgit'''

# Gilgit is the capital of [[Northern Areas]] administrative region of [[Pakistan]], situated near [[Karakoram Highway]] ([[KKH]]). The city is one of the two important hubs for mountaineering expeditions to all peaks in [[Karakoram]] range that includes more than sixty peaks above 7000 m (22,960 ft). The other hub is [[Skardu]].
# Gilgit is one of the six districts of [[Northern Areas]] administrative region of [[Pakistan]].